<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能给我留一点时间吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我需要先思考一下，<delay20 />这股怒意
究竟该如何发泄才好。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～气得不行了！！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能不能请你暂时<delay20 />
不要来打扰我呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我再也忍不下去了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有事找我，能不能晚点再来？<delay40 />
很不凑巧，我现在没那个心情！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />太过分了！<delay frames="40" />
总是摆出一副对我的事情<delay8 />
了如指掌的姿态！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉……怎么能这样<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我只是以自己的方式在享受生活，<delay20 />
为什么非得给我强加其他价值观。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />肯定也有自己的<delay20 />
兴趣或者喜好对不对？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但为什么就是不能理解其他人呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00">购物就是我的兴趣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以要买下喜欢的东西时<delay20 />
都想尽量压得便宜一些。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />却对我说，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />成年人没有必要那么计较，<delay8 />
只要把东西买回来就好了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总觉得心里不是滋味<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是实惠的购物能让我感到愉快罢了！<delay40 />
并不是过得很拮据呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我懂的</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />哦……</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能这么说我真的很感动……<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就知道，<tag a="110" b="4" />你<delay20 />
一定能理解我这种心情的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即便是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />去买东西的时候，
肯定也会觉得<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />便宜的那件
买得更开心啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起一心追着自己想要的东西狂买，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得还是按照自己心中立下的规矩来购物<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更能培养人的生活能力。<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然，“买到”这件事情本身确实非常重要，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但要是能“以合理的价格买到”想要的东西，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能获得更多的喜悦呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很抱歉，<delay20 />
我现在一点都不想<delay20 />
和<tag a="110" b="4" />你说话！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在不想和其他人说话！<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我重新整理好情绪之前，<delay20 />
能不能请你让我独自冷静一下？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在真的<delay20 />非常生气！<delay40 />
所以可不可以<tag a="100" b="0" /><delay8 /><endTag a="100" b="0" />
让我安静一会儿？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你找我有什么事吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最好别忘了<delay8 />
我还在气头上！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉呀</message>
	<message label="203_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />嗯……</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />啊～<delay20 />行了行了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明白了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看起来也有所反省，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这次的事情我可以既往不咎，<delay20 />
但从今往后请你务必注意一点！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～<delay20 />你别摆出这种表情，
我都不知道该怎么办了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且我也想早点和好……<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的事情<delay8 />
就当作没发生过吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
